    "We group together non-commercial and academic-only conditions as the distinction plays a minor role in practice.",
    "We argue in the 'Legal discussion' section that datasets without any licence (unspecified) do not impose any conditions, may be treated as commercially viable, but this assessment depends on a developer's risk tolerance and jurisdiction.",
